020package com.puppycrawl.tools.checkstyle.filters;
021
022/**
023 * An interface for filtering Integer.
024 */
025@FunctionalInterface
026interface IntFilterElement {
027
028    /**
029     * Determines whether or not a filtered Integer is accepted.
030     *
031     * @param intValue the Integer to filter.
032     * @return true if the intValue is accepted.
033     */
034    boolean accept(int intValue);
035
036}
